'''阿德列爾競技場'''（{{lang-ru|Адлер-Арена}}）是一個位於[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]][[索契|索契]]的室內滑冰場。該滑冰場在2012年開始啟用，並容納8000名觀眾。在[[2014年冬季奧林匹克運動會|2014年冬季奧運]]期間，會用作承辦[[競速滑冰|競速滑冰]]的賽事。此前，還曾主辦世界單距離競速滑冰錦標賽及俄羅斯速度滑冰錦標賽。在運動會結束後，該體育館會改造為展覽中心。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.flickr.com/photos/vlad2154/3997669233/ |title=Detailed model of Venue on Sochi Investment Forum 2009 |access-date=2014-01-22 |archive-date=2017-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170225131259/https://www.flickr.com/photos/vlad2154/3997669233/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://sochi2014.com/en/objects/sea/speed_skating/ |title=Sochi2014.com profile |access-date=2014-02-07 |archive-date=2012-03-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120311195625/http://sochi2014.com/en/objects/sea/speed_skating/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="sochi2014">{{cite web|work=Sochi 2014|url=http://www.sochi2014.com/en/games/sport/olympic-games/sports/skating/speed_skating/|publisher=Sochi 2014|title=Olympic Games - Speed Skating|accessdate=27 September 2012|archive-date=2012-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120909064858/http://www.sochi2014.com/en/games/sport/olympic-games/sports/skating/speed_skating/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="AdlerArena"/>

